Package.description: Informatica Cloud Customer 360 is a 100% native Force.com Cloud Application for Master Data Management. Informatica Cloud Customer 360 provides a comprehensive set of Data Management features such as Data Cleansing, Detection and Deduplication of duplicate Accounts, Leads and Contacts in salesforce.com, as well as consolidation and enrichment of data from external systems like SAP, Oracle, Microsoft, or other databases.
